name: Smoke Break
strat: Your whole team must start the round in Hookah and hold it for as long as possible. You may only leave if the spike has been planted.

name: Teleporter guardians
strat: ($randplayer) and ($randplayer) are the teleporter guardians. They must immediately get into the two teleporters as fast as they can. They are not allowed to leave the teleporters and must defend them with their lives.
